Solid construction and reliable design ensure even and continuous flow and spread of materials, eliminating streaks. Its large 4 ft. to 8 ft. spread covers approximately 12,000 sq. ft., so you can cover more ground in much less time quickly and efficiently. Its large, 10 in. x 4 in. turf tread rubber tires provide sure-grip traction and smooth-rolling maneuverability. Item Name: 11 cu. ft. Black Poly Tailgate Salt Spreader
Description: The SaltDogg TGS07 11 cu. ft. Tailgate Spreader is a large volume commercial tailgate spreader. It features a horizontal auger, stainless steel trough and an included concealed vibrator that allows it to spread bulk salt or a sand/salt mix from 3/4-Ton. and 1-Ton. trucks. The spreader has a low-profile, 11 cu. ft. black poly hopper. The hopper's frameless, double-wall poly construction is durable and highly corrosion resistant. The spreader mounts to a 2 in. Item Name: 1.0 cu. yds. Electric Black Poly Hopper Salt Spreader
Description: The SaltDogg SHPE1000 Electric Poly Hopper Spreader gives contractors and property owners a spreader that combines volume with a convenient size. The spreader features a corrosion-resistant 10 cu. ft. poly hopper. It can be easily mounted to a 2 in. Class 4 receiver and also includes a universal stake pocket attachment. The TGS06 is a gravity-fed spreader with a manual open/close gate and an 80 lbs. capacity vibrator to keep material moving. Its 9 in. poly spinner can cast material up to 30 ft. A 1/2 HP, 12-Volt motor is directly wired and controlled by an included variable speed in-cab controller.

Item Name: 22.5 in. 100 lbs. Capacity Grounds Keeper Walk Behind Spreader
Description: The Groundskeeper Walk Behind Broadcast Spreader makes it easy to deice driveways and sidewalks. With an adjustable spread range up to 24 ft. and a 100 lbs. capacity, it's ideal for home owners, property managers and college campuses looking for an efficient way to keep their paths clear. You can cover large areas using bagged salt or ice melt without needing to stop and reload. The manual spreader's 1.67 cu. ft hopper is made of a durable polymer that won't rust or dent. The enclosed gearbox features commercial grade alloy gears and an integrated grease fitting to protect the spreader's moving parts from the elements. The fully welded frame is carbon steel with a corrosion resistant black powder-coated finish. 13 in. pneumatic tires can trudge through snow and over uneven terrain. A fixed rear deflector and 3 adjustable side deflectors allow you to calibrate the spread to your needs. Material flow is controlled with a simple lever for ease of use and the spinner is powered by the movement of the axle for a low maintenance and reliable spread. Please ensure the set screw that attaches the hopper to the spinner is tightly secured for optimal material control. The push spreader comes with a convenient hopper screen and a nylon rain cover to keep your material dry.
